@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h1 class="header-privacy">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    
    <p class="text-privacy">
        Welcome to CarRental. Your privacy matters to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you use our car rental services, website, or mobile applications.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-privacy">
        By using our services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We may collect the following types of personal data:
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        <b>a. Personal Identification Information</b><br />
        Full name<br />
        Date of birth<br />
        Driver’s license details<br />
        Passport or ID number
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        <b>b. Contact Information</b><br />
        Email address<br />
        Phone number<br />
        Address
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        <b>c. Payment Information</b><br />
        Credit/debit card details<br />
        Billing address
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        <b>d. Rental Information</b><br />
        Booking history<br />
        Vehicle preferences<br />
        Pick-up and drop-off locations
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        <b>e. Technical Data</b><br />
        IP address<br />
        Browser type<br />
        Device information<br />
        Cookies and usage data
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We use your data to:<br />
        • Process and manage reservations<br />
        • Verify your identity and driving eligibility<br />
        • Provide customer support<br />
        • Process payments<br />
        • Improve our services and website<br />
        • Send booking confirmations and updates<br />
        • Comply with legal obligations
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We may share your information with:<br />
        • Payment processors<br />
        • Insurance companies (if required)<br />
        • Government or law enforcement authorities (when legally required)<br />
        • Service providers (e.g., IT, customer support)
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We do not sell your personal data to third parties.
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We keep your personal data only as long as necessary to:<br />
        • Fulfill rental agreements<br />
        • Meet legal, tax, or regulatory requirements<br />
        • Resolve disputes
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        Our website uses cookies to:<br />
        • Improve user experience<br />
        • Analyze website traffic<br />
        • Remember your preferences
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        You can control cookies through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">7. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal data, including:<br />
        • Encryption<br />
        • Secure servers<br />
        • Restricted access to data
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        Depending on your location (e.g., GDPR in the EU), you may have the right to:<br />
        • Access your personal data<br />
        • Correct inaccurate data<br />
        • Request deletion of your data<br />
        • Restrict or object to processing<br />
        • Request data portability
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        To exercise your rights, contact us at: carrental@gmail.gr
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        Our website may contain links to external sites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
    </p>

    <h2 class="header-privacy">11. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:
    </p>
    <p class="text-privacy">
        <b>CarRental</b><br />
        Email: carrental@gmail.gr<br />
        Phone: 6947852391<br />
        Address: 10 High Street
    </p>
</div>